OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772745125
OL,3,CWoman died days after telling staff
OL,4,Cshe would 'throw herself into sea'
OL,6,FA woman took her own life days after
OL,7,Ftelling a mental health practitioner
OL,8,Fand a family friend that she would
OL,9,F"throw herself into the sea" if she
OL,10,Fwas left unsupported, an inquest has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FOn Sunday 20 October 2024, 67-year-old
OL,14,FAnne Philomena Potter left her home in
OL,15,FSt Lawrence, Jersey, after insisting
OL,16,Fthat her husband go to the pub to
OL,17,Fwatch the football.
OL,19,FAfter he left, she took two buses to
OL,20,FGreve de Lecq and entered the water.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
