PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772745125
OL,3,CWoman died days after telling staff
OL,4,Cshe would 'throw herself into sea'
OL,6,FHer disappearance sparked a major
OL,7,Fsearch operation, but she could not be
OL,8,Flocated.
OL,10,FWeeks later, her remains were found on
OL,11,Fa beach in Brighton and formally
OL,12,Fidentified last summer.
OL,14,FDays before she vanished, Mrs Potter
OL,15,Fhad been admitted to Jersey's General
OL,16,FHospital and was undergoing treatment
OL,17,Ffor terminal lung cancer.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1772745125
OL,3,CWoman died days after telling staff
OL,4,Cshe would 'throw herself into sea'
OL,6,FThe Coroner, Deputy Viscount Matt
OL,7,FBerry, heard how she had been
OL,8,Fstruggling as her condition
OL,9,Fdeteriorated, and when in hospital,
OL,10,Fshe mentioned to a mental health
OL,11,Fpractitioner that she would end her
OL,12,Flife if discharged without sufficient
OL,13,Fsupport.
OL,15,FDespite this, during an assessment
OL,16,Fwith the crisis team, the court was
OL,17,Ftold how her mood shifted and the
OL,18,Fhealthcare worker believed she was no
OL,19,Flonger a threat to herself, so Mrs
OL,20,FPotter was allowed to return home.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
